article.headline: Texas Tech 74, SE Louisiana 63
article.story: LUBBOCK, Texas -- John Roberson scored 20 points and Alan Voskuil added 18 to lead Texas Tech past Southeastern Louisiana 74-63 on Tuesday night. D'walyn Roberts scored 13 points and had nine rebounds for the Red Raiders (5-0). Brandon Fortenberry led Southeastern Louisiana (1-3) with 13 points, nine of those on 3-pointers. Warrell Span scored 11 points and grabbed 12 rebounds. Chris Cyprina added 10 points. Southeastern Louisiana led 38-37 at the half. The Red Raiders shot 55 percent in the first half after only hitting 42 percent from the field in the first half. Southeastern Louisiana hit only 33 percent in the second half and finished the game with 38 percent from the field.
